experience.description: Worked on a project for a client in the US. The project was to build a web application for the client's customers to manage their accounts. The project was built using ReactJS, TypeScript, Material UI, Tailwind CSS, and other technologies. I was responsible for building the UI of the application and integrating it with the backend APIs. I also worked on the backend APIs using NodeJS, ExpressJS, and MongoDB. I was also responsible for writing unit tests for the UI components using Jest and React Testing Library.
